{
  "name": "BDI ¬∑ F11 Evening Closure Reminder",
  "_meta": {
    "owner": "A6 Fabric (deploy) ¬∑ STU0 (spec)",
    "authority": "D-STU-082 cron schedules + D-STU-088 W25-Q10 Track 3",
    "purpose": "Daily 16:30 PL ¬∑ Slack DM reminder do kaŇľdego employee z F11 enrolled list + post #bdi-daily-closure anchor message ¬∑ KR wrap-up trigger 17:30",
    "schedule": "30 16 * * 1-5 (Europe/Warsaw ¬∑ M-F robocze)",
    "envelope_emits": "control_plane.cp_messages ¬∑ message_type=F11_CLOSURE_REMINDER",
    "consumers": ["#bdi-daily-closure", "Slack DM per enrolled employee", "STU0 OR aggregator", "KR digest input"],
    "sprint": "2 day-2 spec ¬∑ sprint-3 D-X actual n8n deploy"
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "name": "Cron 16:30 PL M-F",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.cron",
      "position": [240, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "triggerTimes": {
          "item": [
            {
              "mode": "everyDay",
              "hour": 16,
              "minute": 30,
              "weekday": "monday,tuesday,wednesday,thursday,friday"
            }
          ]
        },
        "timezone": "Europe/Warsaw"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Fetch F10 posts dziŇõ (correlation)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "position": [440, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "select",
        "tableId": "control_plane.cp_messages",
        "filterUI": {
          "filter": [
            { "column": "message_type", "value": "F10_PRIORITIES" },
            { "column": "created_at", "value": ">={{ $now.startOf('day').toISO() }}" }
          ]
        },
        "credentials": "supabase-prod-service-role"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Post anchor message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "position": [640, 200],
      "parameters": {
        "channel": "#bdi-daily-closure",
        "text": "ūüĆô **F11 Evening Closure ¬∑ {{ $now.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd ¬∑ cccc') }}**\n\nPora na day-end report (target post by 18:00 PL ¬∑ KR wrap-up 17:30-18:00).\n\nTemplate:\n```\nūüĆô F11 ¬∑ {Twoje imińô} ¬∑ {data}\n\nDone dziŇõ (vs morning F10):\n‚úÖ ...\n‚úÖ ...\n‚Ź≥ ... (% done)\n‚ĚĆ ... (pow√≥d)\n\nNiespodzianki dzisiaj:\n- ...\n\nJutro priorytety (preview F10):\n1. ...\n2. ...\n\nEnergy/mood: {1-5} ¬∑ Blockers active: ...\n```\n\nFound {{ $node['Fetch F10 posts dziŇõ (correlation)'].length }} F10 posts dziŇõ ¬∑ correlation auto-linked w cp_messages.",
        "credentials": "slack-bdi-bot"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Loop ¬∑ DM each F10 poster",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "position": [640, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "DM employee F11 reminder",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "position": [840, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "channel": "={{ $json['payload']['employee_id'] }}",
        "text": "ūüĆô **F11 reminder ¬∑ {{ $now.toFormat('cccc dd MMM') }}**\n\n90-min reminder ¬∑ day-end closure (#bdi-daily-closure) target by 18:00 PL.\n\nDziŇõ rano postowaŇāeŇõ F10 ¬∑ jak idzie execution? Niespodzianki?\n\nJeŇõli pracujesz wieczorem ¬∑ post do 22:00 OK ¬∑ NIE codziennie expected.",
        "credentials": "slack-bdi-bot"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Emit cp_message envelope",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "position": [1040, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "insert",
        "tableId": "control_plane.cp_messages",
        "fieldsUI": {
          "fields": [
            { "name": "run_id", "value": "={{ $execution.id }}" },
            { "name": "correlation_id", "value": "={{ $execution.id }}" },
            { "name": "source_workspace", "value": "n8n-WF-F11" },
            { "name": "target_workspace", "value": "BDI-ALL" },
            { "name": "domain", "value": "BDI-GOV" },
            { "name": "actor_type", "value": "N8N" },
            { "name": "actor_id", "value": "n8n.workflow.F11-evening-closure" },
            { "name": "sensitivity_level", "value": "L1_INTERNAL" },
            { "name": "message_type", "value": "F11_CLOSURE_REMINDER" },
            { "name": "payload", "value": "={\"reminded_count\": $node['Fetch F10 posts dziŇõ (correlation)'].length, \"date\": $now.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd')}" }
          ]
        },
        "credentials": "supabase-prod-service-role"
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Cron 16:30 PL M-F": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Fetch F10 posts dziŇõ (correlation)", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Fetch F10 posts dziŇõ (correlation)": {
      "main": [[
        { "node": "Post anchor message", "type": "main", "index": 0 },
        { "node": "Loop ¬∑ DM each F10 poster", "type": "main", "index": 0 }
      ]]
    },
    "Loop ¬∑ DM each F10 poster": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "DM employee F11 reminder", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Post anchor message": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Emit cp_message envelope", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1",
    "errorWorkflow": "wf-error-handler-cp-dlq"
  },
  "active": false,
  "_deploy_notes": "Set active:true after F10 workflow LIVE ¬∑ F11 reads F10 correlation ¬∑ sequence dependency."
}
